Name: TeamID
Description: The auto-generated unique ID of the Team

Name: [Key]
Description: Abbreviation of the team (e.g. LA; PHI; BOS; CHI; etc.)

Name: Active
Description: Whether or not this team is active

Name: City
Description: The city/location of the team (e.g. Los Angeles; Philadelphia; Boston; Chicago; etc.)

Name: Name
Description: The mascot of the team (e.g. Kings; Flyers; Bruins; Blackhawks; etc.)

Name: StadiumID
Description: The unique ID of the team's current home arena

Name: Conference
Description: The conference of the team (possible values: Eastern; Western)

Name: Division
Description: The division of the team (e.g. Atlantic; Metropolitan; etc)

Name: PrimaryColor
Description: The team's primary color. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: SecondaryColor
Description: The team's secondary color. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: TertiaryColor
Description: The team's tertiary color. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: QuaternaryColor
Description: The team's quaternary color. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: WikipediaLogoUrl
Description: The link to the team's logo hosted on Wikipedia. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: WikipediaWordMarkUrl
Description: The link to the team's wordmark logo hosted on Wikipedia. (This is not licensed for public or commercial use)

Name: GlobalTeamID
Description: A globally unique ID for this team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: StadiumID
Description: The unique ID of the arena

Name: Active
Description: Whether or not this arena is the home venue for an active team

Name: Name
Description: The full name of the arena

Name: Address
Description: The address where the arena is located

Name: City
Description: The city where the arena is located

Name: State
Description: The US state where the arena is located (if arena is outside US; this value is NULL)

Name: Zip
Description: The zip code of the arena

Name: Country
Description: The 2-digit country code where the arena is located

Name: Capacity
Description: The estimated seating capacity of the arena

Name: GeoLat
Description: The geographic latitude coordinate of this venue.

Name: GeoLong
Description: The geographic longitude coordinate of this venue.

Name: GameID
Description: The unique ID of this game

Name: Season
Description: The NHL season of the game

Name: SeasonType
Description: The type of season that this record corresponds to (1=Regular Season; 2=Preseason; 3=Postseason; 4=Offseason; 5=AllStar).

Name: Status
Description: Indicates the game's status. Possible values include: Scheduled; InProgress; Final; F/SO; F/OT; Suspended; Postponed; Delayed; Canceled; Forfeit

Name: Day
Description: The date of the game

Name: DateTime
Description: The date and time of the game

Name: Updated
Description: The timestamp of when the record was last updated (US Eastern Time).

Name: IsClosed
Description: Indicates whether the game is over and the final score has been verified and closed out.

Name: AwayTeam
Description: The abbreviation of the Away Team

Name: HomeTeam
Description: The abbreviation of the Home Team

Name: AwayTeamID
Description: The unique ID of the away team

Name: HomeTeamID
Description: The unique ID of the home team

Name: StadiumID
Description: The unique ID of the stadium

Name: Channel
Description: The television station broadcasting the game

Name: Attendance
Description: Total number of people who attended the game

Name: AwayTeamScore
Description: Number of goals the away team scored in this game

Name: HomeTeamScore
Description: Number of goals the home team scored in this game

Name: Period
Description: Indicated the current period of the game. Possible values include: 1; 2; 3; OT; SO; Final; F/OT; F/SO; NULL

Name: TimeRemainingMinutes
Description: Number of minutes that have passed in the current period. Please note this field name is misleading; and actually represents the game clock minutes; which are the number of minutes that have already passed in the period. Possible values: 0-20.

Name: TimeRemainingSeconds
Description: Number of seconds that have passed in the current period. Please note this field name is misleading; and actually represents the game clock seconds; which are the number of seconds that have already passed in the period. Possible values: 0-60.

Name: AwayTeamMoneyLine
Description: Money line from the perspective of the away team.

Name: HomeTeamMoneyLine
Description: Money line from the perspective of the home team.

Name: PointSpread
Description: The oddsmaker Point Spread at game start from the perspective of the HomeTeam (negative numbers indicate the HomeTeam is favored; positive numbers indicate the AwayTeam is favored). This is updated once daily at 4:00 AM ET.

Name: OverUnder
Description: The oddsmaker Over/Under at game start. This is updated once daily at 4:00 AM ET.

Name: GlobalGameID
Description: A globally unique ID for this game. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: GlobalAwayTeamID
Description: A globally unique ID for the away team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: GlobalHomeTeamID
Description: A globally unique ID for the home team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: PointSpreadAwayTeamMoneyLine
Description: The money line payout odds when betting on the away team with the point spread. This is updated once daily at 4:00 AM ET.

Name: PointSpreadHomeTeamMoneyLine
Description: The money line payout odds when betting on the home team with the point spread. This is updated once daily at 4:00 AM ET.

Name: LastPlay
Description: The description of the most recent play/event of the game. This is for display purposes and does not include corresponding data points.

Name: Periods
Description: The details of the periods (including overtime if applicable) for this game.

Name: GameEndDateTime
Description: The date and time that the game ended in US Eastern Time

Name: HomeRotationNumber
Description: The rotation number of the home team for this game

Name: AwayRotationNumber
Description: The rotation number of the away team for this game

Name: NeutralVenue
Description: Indicates whether this game is played in a neutral venue

Name: OverPayout
Description: The payout when betting the Over of the Over/Under

Name: UnderPayout
Description: The payout when betting the Under of the Over/Under

Name: PeriodID
Description: Unique identifier for each period.

Name: GameID
Description: The unique ID for this game.

Name: Name
Description: The Name of the Quarter (possible values: 1; 2; 3; SO; OT; OT2; OT3; OT4; etc)

Name: AwayScore
Description: The total goals scored by the away team in this period.

Name: HomeScore
Description: The total goals scored by the home team in this period.

Name: ScoringPlays
Description: The details of the scoring plays that occurred during this period

Name: Penalties
Description: The details of the penalties that occurred during this period

Name: PlayerID
Description: The player's unique PlayerID as assigned by FantasyData.

Name: FirstName
Description: The first name of the player.

Name: LastName
Description: The last name of the player.

Name: Status
Description: Indicates the player's status of being on an active roster. Possible values include: Active; Inactive

Name: TeamID
Description: The TeamID of the team this player is employed by.

Name: Team
Description: The key/abbreviation of the team this player is employed by.

Name: Position
Description: The player's primary position. Possible values: C; RW; LW; D; or G.

Name: Jersey
Description: The player's jersey number.

Name: Catches
Description: The hand in which the player catches the puck (right or left).

Name: Shoots
Description: The hand the player shoots the puck with (right or left).

Name: Height
Description: The player's height in inches.

Name: Weight
Description: The player's weight in pounds (lbs).

Name: BirthDate
Description: The player's date of birth.

Name: BirthCity
Description: The city in which the player was born.

Name: BirthState
Description: The state in which the player was born.

Name: PhotoUrl
Description: The URL of the player's headshot photo.

Name: SportRadarPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the SportRadar API.

Name: RotoworldPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the Rotoworld news feed.

Name: RotoWirePlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the RotoWire news feed.

Name: FantasyAlarmPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the FantasyAlarm news feed.

Name: StatsPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the STATS data feeds.

Name: SportsDirectPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the SportsDirect data feeds.

Name: XmlTeamPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to the XML Team data feeds.

Name: InjuryStatus
Description: Indicates the player's injury status. Possible values include: Probable; Questionable; Doubtful; Out

Name: InjuryBodyPart
Description: The body part that is injured (Knee; Groin; Calf; Hamstring; etc.)

Name: InjuryStartDate
Description: The day that the injury started or first discovered.

Name: InjuryNotes
Description: Brief description of the player's injury and expected availability.

Name: FanDuelPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to FanDuel.

Name: DraftKingsPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to DraftKings.

Name: YahooPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to Yahoo Daily Fantasy Sports Contests.

Name: FanDuelName
Description: The player's full name in FanDuel's daily fantasy sports platform.

Name: DraftKingsName
Description: The player's full name in DraftKings' daily fantasy sports platform.

Name: YahooName
Description: The player's full name in Yahoo's daily fantasy sports platform.

Name: DepthChartPosition
Description: The position of the player on the depth chart.

Name: DepthChartOrder
Description: The order of the player on the depth chart.

Name: GlobalTeamID
Description: A globally unique ID for this team. This value is guaranteed to be unique across all sports/leagues.

Name: FantasyDraftName
Description: The player's full name in FantasyDraft's daily fantasy sports platform.

Name: FantasyDraftPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to Fantasy Draft.

Name: UsaTodayPlayerID
Description: The player's cross reference PlayerID to USA Today headshot data feeds.

Name: UsaTodayHeadshotUrl
Description: The player's headshot URL as provided by USA Today. License from USA Today is required.

Name: UsaTodayHeadshotNoBackgroundUrl
Description: The player's transparent background headshot URL as provided by USA Today. License from USA Today is required.

Name: UsaTodayHeadshotUpdated
Description: The last updated date of the player's headshot as provided by USA Today. License from USA Today is required.

Name: UsaTodayHeadshotNoBackgroundUpdated
Description: The last updated date of the player's transparent background headshot as provided by USA Today. License from USA Today is required.
